</td></tr></table></div>
<div><a name="_calendar_day_of_year" id="_calendar_day_of_year"></a><h3>4.3.7. Calendar day of year</h3><p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_68ff73a8-717c-4019-a0ff-88c55b3e463c" id="_68ff73a8-717c-4019-a0ff-88c55b3e463c"></a>The calendar day of year is represented as the following time scale component:</p>
<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_121c85d8-ce2f-4e2f-97f3-f46bbf503884" id="_121c85d8-ce2f-4e2f-97f3-f46bbf503884"></a>[i]["O"]</p>
