  <p class="example"><a name="_0c645bcb-613c-4837-aaf2-6ee130c6f558" id="_0c645bcb-613c-4837-aaf2-6ee130c6f558"></a>'351O', ordinal day 351 of the calendar year</p>
</td></tr></table></div>
<div><a name="_clock_hour_and_hours_duration" id="_clock_hour_and_hours_duration"></a><h3>4.3.8. Clock hour and hours duration</h3><p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_1c567d48-d62b-49bf-bf0c-ca60b17bc0bb" id="_1c567d48-d62b-49bf-bf0c-ca60b17bc0bb"></a>Clock hour and hours duration is represented as follows:</p>
<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_fe0bbf75-1eac-47e7-b171-f4358ec81e4f" id="_fe0bbf75-1eac-47e7-b171-f4358ec81e4f"></a>[i]["H"]</p>
