<div><a name="_clock_minute_and_minutes_duration" id="_clock_minute_and_minutes_duration"></a><h3>4.3.9. Clock minute and minutes duration</h3><p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_7596a6f9-6cbf-4263-aeca-4b2a942f2278" id="_7596a6f9-6cbf-4263-aeca-4b2a942f2278"></a>Clock minute and minutes duration is represented as follows:</p>
<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_e9d36ac5-ea24-4049-b4c1-028318d4d22a" id="_e9d36ac5-ea24-4049-b4c1-028318d4d22a"></a>[i]["M"]</p>
<table class="example" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse"><a name="_a3b93737-ed4b-4ad2-aa77-2b3b9ad167ab" id="_a3b93737-ed4b-4ad2-aa77-2b3b9ad167ab"></a><tr><td valign="top" class="example_label" style="width:82.8pt;padding:0 0 0 1em;margin-left:0pt">EXAMPLE  1</td><td valign="top" class="example">
  <p class="example"><a name="_f338738c-a8d7-46a3-a454-5f09cf9aef53" id="_f338738c-a8d7-46a3-a454-5f09cf9aef53"></a>'72M', duration, 72 minutes.</p>
