  <p class="example"><a name="_b85515bb-338a-4837-b9a8-0b8f3d8cb043" id="_b85515bb-338a-4837-b9a8-0b8f3d8cb043"></a>'56M', time, the fifty-sixth clock minute.</p>
</td></tr></table></div>
<div><a name="_clock_second_and_seconds_duration" id="_clock_second_and_seconds_duration"></a><h3>4.3.10. Clock second and seconds duration</h3><p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_856a5bb9-cd8b-4e39-bb31-82ebc0ccf292" id="_856a5bb9-cd8b-4e39-bb31-82ebc0ccf292"></a>Clock second and seconds duration is represented as follows:</p>
<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_856241a2-9637-4ecd-8430-4c094354ffd5" id="_856241a2-9637-4ecd-8430-4c094354ffd5"></a>[i]["S"]</p>
